!docs/assets/screenshots/*.png
# Documentation evidence screenshots. Without these negations `*.png` above
# swallows them silently: `git add` reports nothing and the reference in the
# doc dangles. That is not hypothetical — 147 referenced .png files under
# docs/system-reference/assets/ were lost this way, while every referenced
# .jpg survived, because .jpg was never ignored.
!docs/**/assets/*.png
!docs/**/assets/**/*.png
*.hprof

report.json
.claude/worktrees/

tests/load/results/

